ComicInfo.Summary:
The Stargate Universe comic book picks up the action from right where Season Two of the acclaimed science fiction TV series ended! Want to know what happened to Eli, Doctor Rush, Colonel Young, and the rest of the crew? Pick up this issue of SGU to find out! Stargate Universe comes with three covers, Main Cover by legendary artist Greg LaRocque, a Photo Cover, and an exclusive Retailer Incentive Flashback Photo cover!
